customization/config.html#example.body:
Here’s an example docpress.json:
{
  "docs": "docs",
  "github": "rstacruz/onmount"
}

Or in package.json:
{
  "name": "myproject",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  /* ... */
  "docpress": {
    "github": "rstacruz/myproject"
  }
}

